  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Active nephritis documented by renal biopsy within 24 months of entry;

          2. Failure to respond to 2 or more immunosuppressive regimens which consisted of
             high-dose prednisolone combined with other non-corticosteroid immunosuppressive agents
             together with ACE inhibitors plus or minus angiotensin receptor blockers (ARB) for at
             least 4 months for each regimen at the maximally tolerated drug dosages;

          3. Serum creatinine (Scr) less than 200umol/L.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Previous intolerance to either MMF/Tac;

          2. Scr &gt;200umol/L;

          3. Informed consent unavailable.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
